                                      "content":  {
                                                      "en":  "We stand behind our products and want you to be completely satisfied. If for any reason you are not happy with your purchase, we offer a 30-day hassle-free return policy.\n\nTo initiate a return, please contact us at info@peekeeper.com with your order number and reason for return. Items must be clean, unworn, and in original condition.\n\nOnce your return is received and inspected, we will notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund. Approved refunds will be processed within 5-10 business days to your original payment method.\n\nShipping costs are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error."
                                                  },
                                      "alignment":  "left"
                                  }
                    }
                ]
